{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/GrowingDevlog/20240603_codeBlock_theme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"32's Dev.log","author":"han32","siteUrl":"https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"HSangMi/devlog"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"han32"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d823c39c-037d-5a29-932b-129de68e9fdf","excerpt":"를 사용하고 싶었으나, 적용중인 테마에선 를 사용하고 있었고, 이것저것 시도하다가 결국 을 사용하기로.. 코드블록 테마 바꾸기 우선 플러그인을 설치한다. (사용중인 블로그 템플릿엔 package.json에 이미 있음) 테마를 적용할 두가지 방법을 고려했다 수동으로 prismjs CSS 바꾸기 prismjs 공식 테마 import하기   1. 수동으로 CSS 바꾸기 prism-themes…","html":"<aside>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/JaeYeopHan\">@Jbee</a> 님의 블로그 템플릿을 받아서 사용 중 인데, 코드블록 디자인에 몇가지 설정을 추가하고 싶었다.  <br/>\n<b>1. 테마</b> <br/>\n2. 타이틀 <br/>\n2. 라인넘버 <br/>\n3. 하이라이트  <br/>\n</aside>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-remark-highlight-code</code>를 사용하고 싶었으나, 적용중인 테마에선 <code class=\"language-text\">prismjs</code>를 사용하고 있었고, 이것저것 시도하다가 결국 <code class=\"language-text\">prismjs</code>을 사용하기로..</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"코드블록-테마-바꾸기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9D-%ED%85%8C%EB%A7%88-%EB%B0%94%EA%BE%B8%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"코드블록 테마 바꾸기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>코드블록 테마 바꾸기</h2>\n<p>우선 <code class=\"language-text\">prismjs</code>플러그인을 설치한다. (사용중인 블로그 템플릿엔 package.json에 이미 있음)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> gatsby-remark-prismjs prismjs</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>테마를 적용할 두가지 방법을 고려했다</p>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>수동으로 prismjs CSS 바꾸기</li>\n<li>prismjs 공식 테마 import하기  </li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"1-수동으로-css-바꾸기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EC%88%98%EB%8F%99%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-css-%EB%B0%94%EA%BE%B8%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"1 수동으로 css 바꾸기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 수동으로 CSS 바꾸기</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/PrismJS/prism-themes?tab=readme-ov-file\">prism-themes</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>이 블로그에서 사용하고 있는 템플릿의 기본 코드블록 스타일은 <code class=\"language-text\">prismjs</code>를 기반으로 하고있고 <code class=\"language-text\">styles/code.scss</code>파일에서 커스텀 설정을 하고있다.  </li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">styles/code.scss</code> 파일에 있는 css를 지우고 위 링크에서 맘에드는 테마를 골라 ctrl C V한다.</li>\n<li>공식 테마보다 종류가 많다!<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 513px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"prism-themes\"\n        title=\"prism-themes\"\n        src=\"/devlog/static/6ced250c08f050322608ec1229611648/267f6/prism-theme.png\"\n        srcset=\"/devlog/static/6ced250c08f050322608ec1229611648/5a46d/prism-theme.png 300w,\n/devlog/static/6ced250c08f050322608ec1229611648/267f6/prism-theme.png 513w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 513px) 100vw, 513px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2prismjs-공식-테마-import하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2prismjs-%EA%B3%B5%EC%8B%9D-%ED%85%8C%EB%A7%88-import%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"2prismjs 공식 테마 import하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.prismjs 공식 테마 import하기</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://prismjs.com\">prismjs.com</a> </p>\n<ul>\n<li>prismjs 홈페이지에서 공식 테마를 확인해 볼 수 있다.</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">styles/code.scss</code>의 스타일을 지우고, <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-browser.js</code>에 원하는 테마의 css파일을 적용해준다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">gatsby-browser.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// custom typefaces</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// polyfill</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'intersection-observer'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\"><span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"prismjs/themes/prism-tomorrow.css\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>나는 prismjs 공식 테마를 적용하고 추가적인 커스텀 사항들은 <code class=\"language-text\">styles/code.scss</code>에 추가하여 적용하였다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>코드블록 테두리도 둥글게 만들어주고 ~</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">styles/code.scss</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* code block*/</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">pre[class*=\"language-\"]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> .5em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>다크테마를 적용했더니 <code class=\"language-text\">inline bock</code>이 어둡게 잡히는게 싫어서 아래 css를 추가했다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 241px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 16.182572614107883%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"alt text\"\n        title=\"alt text\"\n        src=\"/devlog/static/1ac4491491da46ebeee4c90401b3e5e0/2f862/inlineblock.png\"\n        srcset=\"/devlog/static/1ac4491491da46ebeee4c90401b3e5e0/2f862/inlineblock.png 241w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 241px) 100vw, 241px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">styles/code.scss</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* Inline code */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">:not(pre)>code[class*=\"language-\"]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> .2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> .3em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">white-space</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> normal<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fff3ce<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #ff5c5c<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"[Gatsby] Prismjs 코드블록 개선(1) 테마","date":"June 03, 2024","tags":["Gatsby","React","prismjs"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/GrowingDevlog/20240603_codeBlock_theme/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Spring/240528_poi_excel_2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[SpringBoot] Apache POI, AbstractView - 엑셀 파일 생성 후 다운로드 (2)","category":"Framework/Spring"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/GrowingDevlog/20240604_codeBlock_title/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Gatsby] Prismjs 코드블록 개선(2) 타이틀 추가하기","category":"Work & Dev/GrowingDevlog"}}}}}